---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Pacific Hearth + Design — Heat & Glo Authorized Dealer | Springfield, OR"
  description="Pacific Hearth + Design is a Platinum-tier Heat & Glo authorized dealer in Springfield, OR. Schedule a free in-home consultation, browse the lineup in their showroom, get installation quotes."
  noIndex={true}
>
  <section class="relative mb-12 -mx-4">
    <img src="https://hearthnhome.getbynder.com/transform/d46ab388-275f-4983-b659-7c4cd454dcf5/img-pdp-mezzo-room-1?io=transform:fill,width:1920,height:720" alt="Pacific Hearth + Design showroom with operating Heat & Glo Mezzo fireplace" class="w-full h-[420px] object-cover" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/85 via-black/65 to-black/30 flex items-end px-8 pb-10">
      <div class="max-w-page mx-auto text-white">
        <p class="uppercase tracking-wide text-sm font-semibold drop-shadow text-orange-300">Authorized Dealer · Platinum Tier</p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mt-2 drop-shadow-lg">Pacific Hearth + Design</h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-lg drop-shadow">Springfield, Oregon · Serving the Willamette Valley since 1998</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="max-w-page mx-auto px-4 py-4">
    <section class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-orange-600 rounded-r p-5 mb-12">
      <p class="text-orange-900 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Demo: Featured Dealer Page</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-800 text-sm">This is a fully-built example of how an individual dealer page renders in the production rollout. Live data on hours, ratings, current inventory, and showroom photography flows through the dealer-management API integration.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-16">
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">About Pacific Hearth + Design</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Pacific Hearth + Design has been the Willamette Valley's specifier-grade Heat & Glo dealer for 27 years. Their Springfield showroom features 14 operating Heat & Glo units across the gas, wood, electric, and outdoor lineup, including the Mezzo, Cosmo, 6K/8K Series, True, and the SupremeX inserts.</p>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">The team specializes in custom residential new-construction and major-renovation installs across Eugene, Springfield, Cottage Grove, and the surrounding region. NFI-certified gas hearth installers on staff. Architect and contractor accounts welcome through the ProAdvantage trade program.</p>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">For commercial and hospitality projects, Pacific Hearth + Design has installed Heat & Glo specifications at boutique hotel properties throughout the Pacific Northwest. Reach out for project references and BIM file access.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-12">In the showroom</h2>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
          <img src="https://hearthnhome.getbynder.com/transform/d46ab388-275f-4983-b659-7c4cd454dcf5/img-pdp-mezzo-room-1?io=transform:fill,width:600,height:600" alt="Mezzo display in Pacific Hearth showroom" class="w-full aspect-square object-cover rounded" />
          <img src="https://hearthnhome.getbynder.com/transform/96f4f3b6-bb4e-4004-a797-85aa7179b3bb/HNG-True_ForgedArch?io=transform:fill,width:600,height:600" alt="True traditional display" class="w-full aspect-square object-cover rounded" />
          <img src="https://hearthnhome.getbynder.com/transform/937081fe-73df-4957-a0ec-8c5a1bfa3a05/HNG-Primo-II_60-2_2?io=transform:fill,width:600,height:600" alt="Primo II see-through display" class="w-full aspect-square object-cover rounded" />
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-12">What buyers say</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-orange-600 pl-6">
            <p class="text-neutral-800 italic mb-2">"They walked us through the lineup over two appointments, helped us narrow to the Mezzo 48 for our great room, and the install crew was exactly when they said they would be. Six months in, no issues."</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">— J. Patterson, Eugene · Mezzo 48 install</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-orange-600 pl-6">
            <p class="text-neutral-800 italic mb-2">"As an architect, I appreciate that their team understands BIM, code reviews, and the difference between a gas insert retrofit and a new-build direct-vent install. Trade account is responsive and well-organized."</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">— A. Mendoza, AIA, Cascade Architecture</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="lg:sticky lg:top-8 lg:self-start space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-4">Visit + Contact</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700 mb-1"><strong>Address</strong></p>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700 mb-3">247 Cascade Avenue<br/>Springfield, OR 97477</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700 mb-1"><strong>Phone</strong></p>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700 mb-3"><a href="tel:5415550142" class="underline">(541) 555-0142</a></p>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700 mb-1"><strong>Hours</strong></p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-700 mb-4">
            <li>Mon-Fri: 9 AM – 6 PM</li>
            <li>Saturday: 10 AM – 4 PM</li>
            <li>Sunday: By appointment</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700 mb-1"><strong>Rating</strong></p>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700 mb-4">⭐ 4.9 · 127 reviews · Google</p>
        </div>

        <a href="tel:5415550142" style="background: #c44a08; color: #fff; display: block; padding: 16px 24px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; text-align: center; text-decoration: none;">Call (541) 555-0142</a>

        <button style="background: #fff; color: #1a1a1a; padding: 16px 24px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; width: 100%; border: 2px solid #1a1a1a; cursor: pointer;">Schedule Consultation →</button>

        <div class="bg-orange-50 border border-orange-200 rounded-lg p-5">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold mb-1">Featured Promotion</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-800">Save up to $650 on a qualifying gas insert through this dealer. <a href="/fireplace-sale/" class="underline font-medium">See terms</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-sm">
          <p class="font-semibold mb-2">Languages spoken</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-700">English, Spanish</p>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>

    <section class="border-t pt-10 mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Featured installations from this dealer</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white border rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <img src="https://hearthnhome.getbynder.com/transform/d46ab388-275f-4983-b659-7c4cd454dcf5/img-pdp-mezzo-room-1?io=transform:fill,width:600,height:400" alt="Eugene great-room Mezzo install" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
          <div class="p-5">
            <p class="font-semibold mb-1">Eugene great room · Mezzo 48</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Custom residential, 2025 install. Stone slab surround, Walnut floating mantel.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <img src="https://hearthnhome.getbynder.com/transform/96f4f3b6-bb4e-4004-a797-85aa7179b3bb/HNG-True_ForgedArch?io=transform:fill,width:600,height:400" alt="Cottage Grove True install" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
          <div class="p-5">
            <p class="font-semibold mb-1">Cottage Grove residence · True 42</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Traditional renovation, 2024 install. Cast Stone surround, Oak corbeled mantel.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <img src="https://hearthnhome.getbynder.com/transform/937081fe-73df-4957-a0ec-8c5a1bfa3a05/HNG-Primo-II_60-2_2?io=transform:fill,width:600,height:400" alt="Springfield see-through install" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
          <div class="p-5">
            <p class="font-semibold mb-1">Springfield residence · Primo II 60 ST</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Living-to-dining see-through partition, 2025 install. Continuous slab stone.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t pt-10">
      <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">
        <a href="/where-to-buy/results/" class="underline">← Back to dealer search results</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
